freesmartphone.org Framework DBus Interface Specification

org.freesmartphone.Resource

Description

This interface provides access to a resource as visible from the OUsage subsystem. If you provide resource to OUsage, you have to implement this interface. Applications usually are not allowed to use this interface.

Namespace

org.freesmartphone.Resource

Methods

  • Enable
  • Disable
  • Suspend
  • Resume

Signals

None

Errors

None

Methods

Enable ( )

Description: Enable the resource.

Disable ( )

Description: Disable the resource.

Suspend ( )

Description: Suspend the resource.

Resume ( )

Description: Suspend the resource.
